---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label" data-animate>About</p>
        <h2 class="heading-section about-heading" data-animate data-delay="1">
          Built for the<br />work that matters.
        </h2>
        <div class="about-body" data-animate data-delay="2">
          <p>
            My background isn't a straight line, and that's the point.
          </p>
          <p>
            I spent six years at Nike managing retail marketing and store design at scale, running $10M+ annual budgets across projects that spanned in-store digital displays, specialty store builds, and brand programs reaching thousands of locations. At Apple, I produced retail experiences end-to-end, from concept through installation, for some of the most scrutinized physical brand environments in the world.
          </p>
          <p>
            That foundation in large-scale execution, stakeholder management, and production under pressure is what I brought into web and digital work when I launched my own practice in 2017. I build websites and digital products the way I managed those projects: with clear scope, strong communication, and an obsession with how the finished thing actually performs in the real world.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now I work with founders, small businesses, and organizations who want that same quality of thinking applied to their digital presence, without the agency overhead.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-image" data-animate data-delay="2">
        <img src="/images/about-headshot.jpg" alt="Shauna" class="about-image-placeholder" />
        <div class="about-image-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <dl class="about-stats" data-animate data-delay="3">
      <div class="stat">
        <dd class="stat-value">10+</dd>
        <dt class="stat-label">Years experience</dt>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <dd class="stat-value">50+</dd>
        <dt class="stat-label">Projects shipped</dt>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <dd class="stat-value">Retail, brand & digital</dd>
        <dt class="stat-label">Focus areas</dt>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <dd class="stat-value">Hawaii / Remote</dd>
        <dt class="stat-label">Location</dt>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
    background: var(--c-bg-subtle);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 55% 45%;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ---- Left: content ---- */
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-heading {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
  }

  .about-body p:first-child {
    color: var(--c-text);
  }

  /* ---- Stats strip ---- */
  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }

  .stat {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--c-text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .stat-rule {
    width: 1px;
    align-self: stretch;
    background: var(--c-border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ---- Right: image ---- */
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-image-rule {
    position: absolute;
    top: -2rem;
    left: 0;
    width: 2px;
    height: calc(100% + 4rem);
    background: var(--c-accent);
  }

  /* ---- Mobile ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-stats {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .stat {
      flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 1rem);
    }

    .stat-rule {
      display: none;
    }

    .about-image {
      padding-left: 0;
      order: 1;
    }

    .about-image-rule {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
